    • 构造器详细资料

      • Builder

        public Builder(int lowerBoundPercent,
               int upperBoundPercent,
               long timeoutInSeconds)
        Creates a new Builder.
        参数:
        lowerBoundPercent - CPU availability lower bound percent.

        CPU availability change notifications are sent when the CPU availability reaches or decreases below this value. The value of this field must be less than the value of mUpperBoundPercent.

        To avoid spurious or very frequent notifications, the delta between the upper bound percent and lower bound percent must be reasonably large.

        To ignore this field, specify CpuAvailabilityMonitoringConfig.IGNORE_PERCENT_LOWER_BOUND as the value. Must not ignore both this field and mUpperBoundPercent in the same configuration.

        upperBoundPercent - CPU availability upper bound percent.

        CPU availability change notifications are sent when the CPU availability reaches or increases above this value. The value of this field must be greater than the value of mLowerBoundPercent.

        To avoid spurious or very frequent notifications, the delta between the upper bound percent and lower bound percent must be reasonably large.

        To ignore this field, specify CpuAvailabilityMonitoringConfig.IGNORE_PERCENT_UPPER_BOUND as the value. Must not ignore both this field and mLowerBoundPercent in the same configuration.

        timeoutInSeconds - CPU availability monitoring timeout in seconds.

        To avoid timing out, specify CpuAvailabilityMonitoringConfig.MONITORING_TIMEOUT_NEVER as the value.
